{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"54854ab0e6","title":"陶鲁笳关于毛泽东“今后不许打人”的传达","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"51e60f53ee","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":20,"articleId":"54854ab0e6","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"陶鲁笳","id":"6a8942ca30","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"4d7666f3fa","name":"陶鲁笳"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"e6af642a86","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54854ab0e6","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1a3de7b5b7","type":"title","text":"陶鲁笳关于毛泽东“今后不许打人”的传达","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54854ab0e6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"461a050413","type":"paragraph","text":"1966年8月21日晚12点20分红卫兵“八·八红旗战斗团”接到北京联络站电文如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54854ab0e6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28f5edc195","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十日晨，陶鲁笳同志接见铁道学院同学，谈到毛主席关于如何对待打人的问题时说，毛主席对片面使用他的话很生气。昨天中央文革小组打电话来说：“好人打坏人活该；坏人打好人，好人光荣；好人打好人误会。”主席说过。主席说，“为什么不把我的话全面谈呢？我后面还有一句话‘今后不许打人’”。陶鲁笳同志说：“今后宣传打人是犯法的。”","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54854ab0e6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8cfc59c55e","type":"paragraph","text":"【另一个说法是：毛的谈话时间为8月2日】","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"54854ab0e6","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}